<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (mntẓrk tẖbt kẖṭwạty .. ʿmr mạ wʿdk lyã kẖạb
 ḥqk dạymaⁿạ nwr lḥyạty .. qlby yạ rby fy ḥbk dạb)2
 ạlqrạr- (ạ̉fkạrk lyã slạm .. htsẖylny kl ạlạ̉yạm)2
 (nfsy ạ̉qwlk ạ̹ny bạḥbk)2 .. ṣdqny ʿjz ạlklạm
 2- mntẓrk rạḥ ạ̉sẖwf ạ̉mjạdk ttḥqq wạlḥzn yzwl
 ywm wrạ ywm rạḥ ạ̉ʿysẖ ạ̉ʿyạdk frḥk jwạyạ ʿly̱ ṭwl 2
 3- mntẓrk wạlrw̉yạ ạ̉mạmy ʿmr mạ ʿyny ʿnhạ tḥyd
 rwḥk ạlṣạlḥ mạsẖy qdạmy bạlnuṣrẗ wyạ ạltạ̉yyd 2
 4- (ʿ ạlmḥrạtẖ ạ̉nạ ḥạṭṭ ạ̹ydy .. wsẖʿạry mbạdy̱ʾ ạlmlkwt
 wysẖrãfny kẖdmẗ sydy .. bjd bạqwlhạ bạ̉ʿly̱ ṣwt)2
 5- (lạ sdwm wʿmwrẗ btḥnyny .. wlạ ybhrny nʿym nuʿmạn
 dạ wjwdk fy ḥyạty ykfyny .. kẖyrk fạyḍ byk sẖbʿạn)2</lyrics>
